comments: Turner (IND) makes contact with Harrell's (LAL) arm and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Schroder's (LAL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
James (LAL) brushes Sabonis' (IND) body after the release of his shot attempt at the basket, and the contact is marginal.
Harrell (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (IND) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Holiday (IND) makes marginal contact with Schroder's (LAL) side when he contests Schroder's driving shot attempt.

As Sabonis (IND) is gathering the ball in the post, James (LAL) makes contact to slightly dislodge it, causing Sabonis to naturally bobble the ball. He then regathers it on his left foot and legally enters his shooting motion.
James (LAL) dislodges the ball from Sabonis (IND) in the post before incidental contact occurs.
Harrell (LAL) makes contact with Sabonis' (IND) wrist and affects his shot near the rim.
Sabonis (IND) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Sabonis (IND) and Kuzma (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Schroder (LAL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Kuzma (LAL) makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (IND) body when he contests Sabonis' shot attempt at the basket
Sabonis (IND) and Kuzma (LAL) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
James (LAL) makes contact with Sabonis' (IND) wrist and affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Kuzma (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Brogdon's (IND) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Turner (IND) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Kuzma's (LAL) hand after his release on his driving shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) deflects the pass attempt to Sabonis' (IND) before incidental contact occurs.
Brogdon (IND) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (LAL).
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) path during the dribble hand-off and marginal contact occurs.
